Environment switching for Snowflake Connector for Python.

Requirements
============

Requires Python 3.6 or above.

Usage
=====

You can install snowenv from `PyPI`_:

.. _`PyPI`: https://pypi.org/project/snowenv/

.. code-block:: shell

    pip install snowenv

Code of Conduct
